# Renovate

Renovate is a tool for keeping source code dependencies up to date by scanning a repo for package manager files and submitting Pull Requests with upated versions whenever they are found.

 * [Documentation](https://docs.renovatebot.com/)

 Operations Engineering can add or remove renovate on a repo, please submit a request via our Slack channel[#ask-operations-engineering](https://mojdt.slack.com/archives/C01BUKJSZD4)
